OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,FA deal has been reached between
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council and Unite the
OL,8,FUnion that will bring the 16-month bin
OL,9,Fstrike to an end.
OL,11,FCllr John Cotton, the Leader of
OL,12,FBirmingham City Council said a
OL,13,F"negotiated settlement to end the bin
OL,14,Fstrike is now within sight".
OL,16,FIn a statement, he said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,F"This has been a challenging and
OL,7,Fcomplex process, but after months of
OL,8,Fhard work, on the principles and
OL,9,Fparameters of a deal, I believe a new
OL,10,Fimproved offer can be made and terms
OL,11,Fcan be put in place that address the
OL,12,F"ballpark issues" discussed at ACAS
OL,13,Fthat Unite members can agree in order
OL,14,Fto end the strike once and for all.
OL,16,F"A deal that would be good for the
OL,17,Fworkforce, represent good value for
OL,18,Fmoney and would not repeat the
OL,19,Fmistakes of the past and risk creating
OL,20,Fnew structural equal pay liabilities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUtD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,F"I want our workforce to be able to
OL,7,Freturn to work and help us deliver the
OL,8,Fquality refuse and recycling services
OL,9,Fthe people of this city deserve.
OL,11,F"That's why throughout this dispute I
OL,12,Fhave resisted those who would dismiss
OL,13,Fthe striking workers instead of
OL,14,Fnegotiating.
OL,16,F"I have instructed officers to move
OL,17,Fforward with negotiations so that we
OL,18,Fcan bring this matter to a close.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,F"Whilst the pre-election period
OL,7,Fprevents the Council from making a
OL,8,Ffinal decision prior to 7 May, a re-
OL,9,Felected Labour administration under my
OL,10,Fleadership will work to get this deal
OL,11,Fapproved as a matter of absolute
OL,12,Fpriority.
OL,14,F"The council can then move forward and
OL,15,Foffer the people of Birmingham the
OL,16,Fservices that they deserve.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,F"I also want to re-emphasise my
OL,7,Fabsolute determination to see through
OL,8,Fthe agreement reached with the
OL,9,Fcouncil's unions last year that will
OL,10,Fdeliver the pay justice that thousands
OL,11,Fof women workers were denied under
OL,12,Fprevious leaderships.
OL,14,F"I would like to thank the people of
OL,15,FBirmingham for their patience during
OL,16,Fthis challenging time.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,F"It's now clear that whilst other
OL,7,Fparties have no plan, only Labour can
OL,8,Fend this dispute and deliver a refuse
OL,9,Fservice that works for everyone in
OL,10,FBirmingham."
OL,12,FUnite the Union says there will now be
OL,13,Fa series of meetings to complete the
OL,14,Foffer.
OL,16,FIt has warned that if the deal is
OL,17,Freneged on in any way, the dispute
OL,18,Fwill be escalated.
OL,20,F"A vindication of the bin workers'
OL,21,Fstruggle for a decent deal"
OL,26,@rD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
