CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid:
OL,9,F"As I have said on many occasions, the
OL,10,Fworkers come first and we will always
OL,11,Fdo everything in our power to ensure
OL,12,Fthat our members are treated with
OL,13,Fdignity and respect.
OL,15,F"The move made today by the leader of
OL,16,Fthe council is a vindication of the
OL,17,Fbin workers' struggle for a decent
OL,18,Fdeal.
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,F"Over the last few months, there have
OL,7,Fbeen intense negotiations to get the
OL,8,Fblocked "ballpark" deal back on the
OL,9,Ftable, so that our members could vote
OL,10,Fon it.
OL,12,F"The reason why we are not yet at that
OL,13,Fstage is purely down to the vindictive
OL,14,Finterference of the government backed
OL,15,Fcommissioners who have attempted to
OL,16,Fblock the deal again and clearly
OL,17,Foverstepped their remit.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IOUpD@RO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,F"Their lack of both experience and
OL,7,Findustrial relations competence has
OL,8,Fbeen a major factor in this dispute,
OL,9,Fand their malevolent game playing has
OL,10,Fbeen an absolute disgrace.
OL,12,F"The commissioner model is a licence
OL,13,Ffor a few unelected individuals to
OL,14,Fprint money and play games.
OL,16,F"They have let the workers down, the
OL,17,Fpeople of Birmingham down and the
OL,18,Fcouncil down.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,F"I salute the fortitude of my members
OL,7,Fwho have needlessly been forced to
OL,8,Fendure months of attacks and hardship
OL,9,Fto get us to this point.
OL,11,F"I thank mayor Richard Parker and Lord
OL,12,FBrendan Barber for the important roles
OL,13,Fboth have played in getting us to this
OL,14,Fpoint.
OL,16,F"And I thank the people of Birmingham
OL,17,Ffor their continued patience and
OL,18,Fsupport."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/19
