OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,FUnion members in Birmingham started an
OL,7,Fall-out strike in March last year in a
OL,8,Fdispute over pay, with little or no
OL,9,Fsign of a deal to end the deadlock
OL,10,Fsince then.
OL,12,FThe union says planned reforms of the
OL,13,Frefuse collection service will lead to
OL,14,Fhundreds of its members losing
OL,15,Fthousands of pounds.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,FIn March the council revealed new bins
OL,7,Fwill be delivered to residents in
OL,8,FBirmingham, as it prepares to roll out
OL,9,Fpromised improvements to its refuse
OL,10,Fcollection service, despite the year-
OL,11,Flong strike by some of its workers.
OL,13,FA long-running dispute
OL,15,FWhat are the main political parties
OL,16,Fsaying?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,FLabour: The Labour-led council insists
OL,7,Fit wants a negotiated settlement. The
OL,8,Fcouncil walked away from formal
OL,9,Fnegotiations last July, arguing it had
OL,10,Freached the limit of what it could
OL,11,Foffer. Its legal advice suggests that
OL,12,Fagreeing to a one-off payment, a key
OL,13,Fdemand from workers seeking to offset
OL,14,Fwage losses reportedly worth thousands
OL,15,Fof pounds a year, could trigger
OL,16,Ffurther equal pay liabilities.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,FReform UK: Reform says it would "re-
OL,7,Festablish negotiations effectively and
OL,8,Fin good faith" and says it has already
OL,9,Fheld discussions with Unite. Candidate
OL,10,FJex Parkin argues that its candidates
OL,11,Fare doctors, nurses and business
OL,12,Fowners with "real world experience"
OL,13,Fthat would strengthen the council's
OL,14,Fnegotiating position.The party's key
OL,15,Fproposal is to review the legal advice
OL,16,Fthat currently underpins the council's
OL,17,Fstance.
OL,26,@nD@aOUpD@NO]tD@MOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,FConservatives: Conservative leader
OL,7,FRobert Alden says senior figures must
OL,8,Fbe directly involved in negotiations.
OL,9,FThe party says the council cannot
OL,10,Fsimply concede to union demands if
OL,11,Fdoing so would breach equal pay law.
OL,12,FBut, like others, they argue that
OL,13,Fwithout direct engagement, a legally
OL,14,Fsound compromise will never be found.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,FLiberal Democrats: The Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrats echo the call to "work
OL,8,Fthrough the differences" between the
OL,9,Ftwo sides, particularly around their
OL,10,Fconflicting legal interpretations. In
OL,11,Fthe longer term, they suggest a more
OL,12,Fstructural solution. This would
OL,13,Finvolve splitting waste services into
OL,14,Fmultiple contracts and outsourcing
OL,15,Fthem, shifting equal pay risks onto
OL,16,Fprivate providers. That may offer a
OL,17,Ffuture model, but it does little to
OL,18,Fresolve the immediate dispute.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,FGreen Party: The Greens argue the
OL,7,Fcouncil has been "negligent" in
OL,8,Fallowing negotiations to stall since
OL,9,Flast summer. When pressed on the
OL,10,Fcouncil's legal position, they point
OL,11,Fto Unite's opposing advice, suggesting
OL,12,Fthe authority under them might give
OL,13,Fgreater weight to the union's case."We
OL,14,Fneed to listen to the other side
OL,15,Fmore," says candidate Julien
OL,16,FPritchard. That raises a key question.
OL,17,FWould a Green-led council be prepared
OL,18,Fto set aside its own legal advice in
OL,19,Ffavour of the union's interpretation?
OL,26,@uD@dOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
