OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe bin strike is shaping how people
OL,12,Fin Birmingham plan to vote in next
OL,13,Fmonth's local elections, according to
OL,14,Fa new ITV News Central poll.
OL,16,FThe survey of 871 residents suggests
OL,17,Flocal frustrations are dominating the
OL,18,Fpolitical agenda in the UK's second
OL,19,Fcity - with the bin dispute emerging
OL,20,Fas the single biggest issue facing
OL,21,Fvoters.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G18/19
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
