PN,37219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777309555
OL,3,CBirmingham bin strikes to end after
OL,4,Cagreement reached with union
OL,6,FAlmost six in ten people (59%) said
OL,7,Fresolving the strike is one of their
OL,8,Ftop priorities, and almost two-thirds
OL,9,F(63%) said it will directly influence
OL,10,Fhow they vote.
OL,12,FUnion boss admits to fresh "talks"
OL,13,Fwith council over Birmingham bin strike
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G19/19
